00:28:38.792 --> 00:28:40.515
- Does it take 10 years to become a priest?
- Around 10 years.

455
00:28:40.547 --> 00:28:44.143
- They’re married for 10 years?
- Yes, they've been married for 10 years.

456
00:28:44.168 --> 00:28:47.794
- And they still don't have a child?
See, Jaime's really infertile.

