00:29:18.027 --> 00:29:21.948
I mean what do you need to show,
he's just saying...

465
00:29:23.784 --> 00:29:27.044
The monsignor just keeps
 telling him she’s married.

466
00:29:27.069 --> 00:29:29.279
For him to stop everything.

