00:29:31.162 --> 00:29:33.315
- That's where I got--
- In the scene where they got caught?

468
00:29:33.370 --> 00:29:34.370
That part.

469
00:29:35.145 --> 00:29:37.770
Afterwards,
Victor was very defiant.

470
00:29:38.061 --> 00:29:42.880
"No, I won't leave Sarah.
I've made my choice."

471
00:29:43.145 --> 00:29:45.228
"I'll leave priesthood behind."

472
00:29:45.317 --> 00:29:47.731
Of course, the monsignor
is shocked to hear this.

473
00:29:48.052 --> 00:29:49.755
Then after that,

474
00:29:50.141 --> 00:29:52.846
the scene ended just like that,
with Sarah leaving

475
00:29:53.214 --> 00:29:55.964
and Victor determined

476
00:29:56.614 --> 00:29:59.964
to get out of priesthood
for Sarah.

477
00:30:01.588 --> 00:30:03.962
But after that Victor goes,

478
00:30:04.009 --> 00:30:06.703
"Go ahead Father, scold me. Swear at me."

479
00:30:07.458 --> 00:30:09.428
It's like, wait a minute.

480
00:30:09.653 --> 00:30:12.968
The monsignor was probably thinking,
"I thought you were already leaving?"

481
00:30:14.601 --> 00:30:20.248
I’m confused because the issue
keeps on repeating

482
00:30:20.273 --> 00:30:23.185
instead of moving forward.

483
00:30:24.021 --> 00:30:25.482
- It could be...

484
00:30:26.121 --> 00:30:32.317
