00:30:33.007 --> 00:30:36.056
That's a possibility.
You could connect it there.

486
00:30:37.263 --> 00:30:38.385
Could be.

487
00:30:39.255 --> 00:30:40.746
But you should remove the

488
00:30:40.840 --> 00:30:44.652
"When I was young..." and so on part.

489
00:30:44.731 --> 00:30:47.832
Go directly to your moth metaphor,

490
00:30:47.930 --> 00:30:50.668
like whatever you're going to do

491
00:30:51.688 --> 00:30:54.731
will burn you in the end.
Something like that.

492
00:30:55.764 --> 00:31:02.020
Although I really want you
to look for another metaphor,

493
00:31:02.052 --> 00:31:03.686
- because that one's already--
